definition: Performance counter timestamp from python's time.perf_counter_ns()

Debug log event in the adaptive sampling script. Possible values: Raw_data_received_from_MinKNOW_API, Raw_data_packaged, Raw_data_sent_to_basecaller, Read_received_from_basecaller, Decision_made_and_action_generated, Action_sent, Action_response_received, Failed_to_send_to_basecaller
